# 01 — Convert GeoMx WTA Data to AnnData

This notebook converts NanoString GeoMx WTA count matrices into a structured AnnData object for downstream Bayesian spatial deconvolution.

The AnnData object will store:

- WTA target gene counts in `adata.X`
- raw counts in `adata.layers["counts"]`
- ROI metadata in `adata.obs`
- gene annotations in `adata.var`
- negative probe counts in `adata.obsm["negProbes"]`
Cell 2 — Code
import scanpy as sc

from python.geomx_anndata_utils import (
    build_geomx_wta_anndata,
    split_anndata_by_obs
)
